    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Shields of Loyalty》是一款回合制黑暗奇幻策略游戏。背景设定在一个受经典作品启发的主题2D世界，结合了现代特色与玩法。在曼塔利亚群岛上体验具有高挑战性和高重玩价值的TBS战斗，引领你的军队从一场战斗走向另一场胜利！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318240/extras/05f404da70810474fdf2e3ca4cb41625.poster.avif?t=1766156555\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318240/extras/05f404da70810474fdf2e3ca4cb41625.webm?t=1766156555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318240/extras/05f404da70810474fdf2e3ca4cb41625.mp4?t=1766156555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>自定义你的军队</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >指挥三位独特头像之一，每位都拥有不同的技能和光环来塑造你的战略：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>高贵的阿格洛万：</strong> 一位不祥的骑兵统帅，擅长发动迅速而强大的攻击。凭借他的威严气场，召集多样化部队，用光环主宰战场。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>战争领主卡尔诺斯：</strong> 专注于蛮力与战术支配的蛮族首领。率领强大的步兵和飞行单位，用压倒性的力量击溃敌人。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>萨尔贡一世：</strong> 一位施法指挥官，能够强化以魔法为主的军队。他的存在增强了盟军的魔法，并减少所受魔法伤害，率领沙漠秘法师和强大战力。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >训练你的部队，使其成长为更强大的士兵。收集神器进一步增强力量并解锁特殊技能。明智地运用它们，击败邪恶军团，赢得胜利！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>体验战术深度</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用每位头像和英雄的独特光环在战斗中取得优势。解放“古代战争的英雄”，并将他们的力量用于你的战术！</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在地形上布置战略阵型，以克服挑战和障碍。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将部队编组成更大的队伍，与强敌对抗并抵御邪恶的猛攻。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318240/extras/7dab274faa03b8543659de5823a792d4.poster.avif?t=1766156555\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318240/extras/7dab274faa03b8543659de5823a792d4.webm?t=1766156555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318240/extras/7dab274faa03b8543659de5823a792d4.mp4?t=1766156555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索多样化生物群落</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在多个动态区域中与不死军团作战：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>黑暗森林：</strong> 在森林、沼泽和岩石地形覆盖的区域开启你的战役。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>永恒冰原：</strong> 前进到充满致命陷阱的雪地冻原。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>熔岩沙漠：</strong> 进入炽热的熔岩地带，环境危机为你提供新的战术机会和敌人。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>应对环境效果</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >生存下来，面对随机生成的环境效果，如雷击、风暴或陨石。这些事件不分敌我，都会毫不留情地打击！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318240/extras/d3709062a0feaf8555a3cf9c1cb28198.poster.avif?t=1766156555\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318240/extras/d3709062a0feaf8555a3cf9c1cb28198.webm?t=1766156555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318240/extras/d3709062a0feaf8555a3cf9c1cb28198.mp4?t=1766156555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>重玩价值</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在解放曼塔利亚的道路上，做出决定以解锁某些关卡而封锁其他关卡。一次又一次地投入战斗，体验全部挑战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318240/extras/ddd722af8b8853b5426b6cd3fed9d60e.poster.avif?t=1766156555\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318240/extras/ddd722af8b8853b5426b6cd3fed9d60e.webm?t=1766156555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318240/extras/ddd722af8b8853b5426b6cd3fed9d60e.mp4?t=1766156555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
